definitions.definition: To eject abruptly ; to throw out suddenly and swiftly.
To eject or suddenly throw fluid or some other substance from a duct or other body structure.
Of a human being or other mammal : to forcibly eject from the urethra in response to sexual stimulation , in a male, semen ; and, in a female, vaginal fluid .
examples: Men can ejaculate between 0.1 and 10 milliliters of semen on average.
With a groan, he ejaculated on his abdomen.

definitions.definition: To sexually stimulate (someone) so that they eject fluid from the urethra.

main_definition: ( transitive ) To eject abruptly ; to throw out suddenly and swiftly.
